OL,5,G1235 All Creatures Great and Small:
OL,6,G     Christmas Special
OL,7,     FIn this holiday special, James is
OL,8,     Ftrying to bury his pain over Helen
OL,9,     Fand has invited his new girlfriend
OL,10,     FConnie to the annual Skeldale
OL,11,     FChristmas party.
OL,12,G1355 All Creatures Great and Small
OL,13,     FIt's spring in 1938, and James's
OL,14,     Fparents are overjoyed when he's
OL,15,     Foffered a position at his old
OL,16,     Fmentor's forward-thinking practice
OL,17,     Fin Glasgow.
