OL,14,     Fnear-fatal fall from a balcony
OL,15,     Fduring a fashion show, Jean
OL,16,     Fapproaches two suspects. But
OL,17,     FViolet's attempted murder is just
OL,18,     Fthe tip of the iceberg...
